data.description: CHARMING 4 BEDROOM 2 BATH HOME! Move In Ready!!  Located just outside of Farmville, VA on 1.60 acres. This home has all the interior features you have come to expect from a Rock River Home including Granite Counters, Large Kitchen island, Stainless Appliances, Drop Zone in Laundry Room, Wood Floors, Cathedral Ceilings, Stone Fireplace with built ins. The First Floor Master Bedroom has an En Suite & WIC. Master Bath has Double Vanity, Tile Flooring & Tiled Shower. Exterior includes a Covered Front Stamped Concrete Patio, plus a Large Rear Deck.
